{"tid":1603319,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[行動PO] 好多人問10.1應該點做先好？當然係各區商場高唱國歌，表達愛國之情了","createTime":"2019-09-29T15:59:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T00:00:22.000Z","uid":54684,"like":6,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"95604e5d9d8e90b35bce1d68dbd9c097f28e3627","tid":1603319,"uid":54684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:59:35.000Z","msg":"<ins>經過今日，好多人都好worry，好想跳出呢個LOOP</ins><br />\n<br />\n好多人問，&quot;喂，10.1應該點做先好？&quot;<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我會話，當然係各區高唱國歌，表達愛國之情了</span></strong><br />\n咁邊度唱先好？咁就梗係各區既商場室內了，街上天氣太熱<br />\n<em><span style=\"color: blue;\">狂唱歌，狂愛國，不用上街，不用衝突</span></em><br />\n<br />\n<strong>好處</strong><br />\n- 目標明確，表現自我身份，不是衝突，不是repeat風險<br />\n<strong>- 傳媒主要拍到既係唱歌，係一種身份既彰顯，不是衝突畫面</strong><br />\n- Singing Contest，和理非一同參與，人數很多<br />\n- 冷氣舒服，可長期進行<br />\n- 多區商場一齊唱？人數就多了，必定成為佳話，而且分開多區，不聚一處，風險都少了<br />\n- 反對暴徒，愛護自由！意思都帶出來了<br />\n- 有無卡牌標語？都可以拎來<br />\n- 唱完返屋企要點？當然係上Twitter話畀全世界聽，話畀Solomon Yue, Marco Rubio, Nancy Pelosi了，<strong>hashtag: #HongKongAnthem </strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>問題</strong><br />\nQ1. 如果有廢老唔愛國，走來搞對台，打人，製造事端，再call警察咁又點呀？<br />\nA1. 避戰係最主要手段，要分隔大家，大家singing contest歌唱比賽，鬥下唱功無問題，反正我地win硬，最緊要EQ要提升到極高，記住大家係來唱歌，唔係為啖氣<br />\n<br />\nQ2. 如果真係有警察來阻止大家表達愛國，話不允許活動咁點呀？<br />\nA2. 古語有云 BE WATER，話得WATER當然隨時走動。大家愛國人士，一定合作係咪？走咪走，落街去第2度唱過。一路行，一路唱。<strong>不死守，話走就走，話聚就聚</strong>，一定以合法方式表達愛國之情，喂個區有好多地方/室內架嘛<br />\n<br />\nQ3. 咩商場好啊？<br />\nA3. 當然愈大愈好了，愈多鏡頭愈好，個shot愈靚愈好，呢個performance係全球直播架<br />\n<br />\nQ4. 會唔會有今日既場面架？<br />\nA4. 大家要<strong><ins>目標清晰</ins></strong>，出來係為咩？想當天回家，見到新聞報咩？有咩效果？記住同上同落，不被捕，積極思考唔同類型既方法。BE WATER就係不硬碰，<strong>看似極柔極廢，但效果要更突出，身份更明顯</strong><br />\n<br />\nQ5. 會唔會有人搞商舖架？<br />\nA5. 唔好啦，可以一齊唔幫襯佢，搞舖其實作用不大，一齊唔幫襯佢咪好<br />\n<br />\nQ6. 咩鐘數呀？持續幾耐？<br />\nA6. 大家諗啦，過度耐又可能有風險，亦可能唔夠人"},{"pid":"9ed064498395bb3100f0e673856c92477010bfde","tid":1603319,"uid":54684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T16:00:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75727d844ca0ae4ab18c63d76dcd005d5dd70179","tid":1603319,"uid":54684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T16:02:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52f596fec471166453648ea05554235864694f42","tid":1603319,"uid":54684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T16:08:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca8d5b572729f29a5ffc854d884e982592ba71af","tid":1603319,"uid":54684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T16:27:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77dee3329cf8d2289610b9e1453023ad13c2ef36","tid":1603319,"uid":54684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T16:53:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb95bd7aea77bccab4c3a9cc4c9c96652d13bc35","tid":1603319,"uid":54684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T17:01:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"715a13395a404fad5b9149dc34251addafb9bce7","tid":1603319,"uid":80972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T19:37:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6353112e773a6b4cb64d47364e968c607582683d","tid":1603319,"uid":80972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T19:37:50.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a7bde49f1e9486b866dec5a36386907106d9c62c","tid":1603319,"uid":80972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T23:46:51.000Z","msg":"百幾萬理和非要出黎呀"},{"pid":"0e5cfc0a292fe03b5d648cb45784be634ba78952","tid":1603319,"uid":6594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T00:00:22.000Z","msg":"唔好落中共面？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nGxqTPK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u